name: LA LUNA  -  3/4 MAJOR ARCANA
description:
XVIII.  LA LUNA

In the darkness of the night, dive into yourself and grasp that pearl that holds your fears. Hold it tightly in your claws; you have to know it, it's the only way to bring them to light and let them go.

 - In 2019 I created my first tarot deck: El Tarot de la Fuerza, this collection of MAJOR ARCANA is part of its second edition -
